# Everything here is excluded from the build CONTEXT — the tarball Docker uploads to the
# daemon before it runs a single instruction. Keep it small, and keep secrets out of it.
#
# Note what is NOT listed: fx-monitor and fx-orchestrator. They are SIBLINGS of this folder,
# not children, so they were never in this build context to begin with. Laying the three apps
# out side by side is what keeps each build context naturally small.
target/
.git/
.github/
.idea/
*.iml
docs/
README.md
